Have you heard?

20
00:04:21,910 --> 00:04:24,130
The leader of the Sigu Sect, Li Xiangyi, is not dead.

21
00:04:24,330 --> 00:04:24,940
Really?

22
00:04:24,960 --> 00:04:25,520
Yes.

23
00:04:26,420 --> 00:04:28,100
The traitor, Yun Biqiu,

24
00:04:28,400 --> 00:04:30,390
conspired with Jiao Liqiao repeatedly

25
00:04:30,500 --> 00:04:32,180
and almost overturned the whole martial world.

26
00:04:32,330 --> 00:04:34,610
Fortunately, the Sigu Sect leader,

27
00:04:34,630 --> 00:04:35,529
Li Xiangyi, resurfaced the martial world

28
00:04:35,690 --> 00:04:37,290
and curbed the chaos.

29
00:04:37,420 --> 00:04:39,600
I heard that the Sigu Sect is going to interrogate the traitor, Yun Biqiu.

30
00:04:39,820 --> 00:04:41,570
Why don't we witness it together?

31
00:04:41,650 --> 00:04:42,020
Let's go.

32
00:04:42,020 --> 00:04:42,780
I'll go with you.

33
00:04:42,780 --> 00:04:43,300
Let's go.

34
